    de.gmxhome.conrad.jpos.jpos_base
     
  • Klasse
    Beschreibung
    Factory
    General part of FiscalPrinterService factory for JPOS devices using this framework.
    FiscalPrinterErrorEvent
    FiscalPrinter error events, holds additional parameters.
    FiscalPrinterException
    Fiscal printer exception class.
    FiscalPrinterInterface
    Interface for methods that implement property setter and method calls for the FiscalPrinter device category.
    FiscalPrinterProperties
    Class containing the FiscalPrinter specific properties, their default values and default implementations of FiscalPrinterInterface.
    FiscalPrinterService
    FiscalPrinter service implementation.
    FiscalPrinterStatusUpdateEvent
    Status update event implementation for FiscalPrinter devices.
    FiscalPrinterToDecimalWrapper
    Wrapper class as interface between applications and services which use different kinds of currency-to-string conversion.
    FiscalPrinterToIntegerWrapper
    Wrapper class as interface between applications and services which use different kinds of currency-to-string conversion.
    OutputRequest
    Output request class for fiscal printers.
    PrePostOutputRequest
    Output request base for FiscalPrinter methods that use properties PreLine and / or PostLine.
    PrintFiscalDocumentLine
    Output request executor for FiscalPrinter method PrintFiscalDocumentLine.
    PrintFixedOutput
    Output request executor for FiscalPrinter method PrintFiscalDocumentLine.
    PrintNormal
    Output request executor for FiscalPrinter method PrintNormal.
    PrintRecCash
    Output request executor for FiscalPrinter method PrintRecCash.
    PrintRecItem
    Output request executor for FiscalPrinter method PrintRecItem, output request base for several PrintRec... methods with quantity and price data.
    PrintRecItemAdjustment
    Output request executor for FiscalPrinter method PrintRecItemAdjustment.
    PrintRecItemAdjustmentVoid
    Output request executor for FiscalPrinter method PrintRecItemAdjustmentVoid.

    PrintRecPackageAdjustment

    PrintRecPackageAdjustVoid
